#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:435
msgid "Now that we are free, together we can defeat our oppressors!"
msgstr "現在我們自由了，我們可以一起擊敗他們！"

